text: This section describes the HTTP/2 agents. The HTTP/2 Server and Client agents are for real-time workflows. The Open API and 5G Profiles can be used with HTTP/2 agents. Open It also includes APL functions for connecting as a client to an external HTTP/2 server. Note! The HTTP/2 Agent code is refactored from MediationZone versions 8.1.9 and 8.2, 10.6. This section contains the following subsections: HTTP/2 Server Agent HTTP/2 Client Agent HTTP/2 UDRs 5G UDRs
title: HTTP/2 Agents - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
